<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="ops-shell page-stack">
    <view class="card intro-card">
      <view class="page-title">业务维护</view>
      <view class="text-body">你好，{{displayName || '房东'}}。所有维护动作统一在这里执行，首页只承担经营盘面与提醒入口。</view>
      <view class="text-muted">维护入口固定：快速录入、房源维护、租约维护。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="card action-card quick-card">
      <view class="section-head-main">
        <view class="section-title">快速录入</view>
        <view class="text-muted">适合新增房源并快速形成可管理房间与租约的轻流程。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="action-buttons">
        <button class="primary-button" data-url="/pages/quick-entry/index" bindtap="navigateTo">打开快速录入</button>
        <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="openUnitsTab">前往房源列表</button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card action-card">
      <view class="section-head-main">
        <view class="section-title">维护中心</view>
        <view class="text-muted">按对象维护基础资料，保证提醒、列表与详情链路数据完整。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="ops-grid">
        <button class="secondary-button" data-url="/pages/assets-form/index" bindtap="navigateTo">房源维护</button>
        <button class="secondary-button" data-url="/pages/leases-form/index" bindtap="navigateTo">租约维护</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
